===Adjective===
{{en-adj-more}}; (''slang comparative'' '''[[funner]]''', ''slang superlative'' '''[[funnest]]'''; ''see usage notes below'')

#(''informal'') [[enjoyable]], [[amusing]]
#:''We had a fun time at the party.''
#:''He is such a fun person to be with.''

====Usage notes====
*For more on the slang comparative and superlative, the use of which is disputed, see [http://www.worldwidewords.org/qa/qa-fun1.htm this discussion]
*Note that the use of ''fun'' as an adjective is never considered acceptable in formal writing.

